==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inexactitude
<hw>In`ex*act"i*tude</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Inexactness; uncertainty; <as>as, geographical
<ex>inexactitude</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Something inexact; an instance of an inexact
statement, measurement, etc.; <as>as, in two minutes the senator has
produced a dozen <ex>inexactitudes</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inexactly</ent>⟦br⟧
